item.title: Random bits
item.description:
This are mine random bits for my first posting.

My Debian QA page(http://qa.debian.org/developer.php?login=zlatan.todoric%40gmail.com)

* Randomness

Debian

Half a bee, philosophically, must ipso facto half not be.
But half the bee has got to be, vis-a-vis its entity.  See?
But can a bee be said to be or not to be an entire bee,
When half the bee is not a bee, due to some ancient injury?
